dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v2.systemtemplate.fibex.fibex4flexray.flexraytopology

Interface IFlexrayFifoConfiguration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IFlexrayFifoConfiguration
extends IEntity
    IFlexrayFifoConfiguration: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    One First In First Out (FIFO) queued receive structure, defining the admittance criteria to the FIFO, and mandating the ability to admit messages into the FIFO based on Message Id filtering criteria.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
